stable.body:
### üí• BREAKING CHANGES
- due to [`dd8f665`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/dd8f665b227866d4577eb97f44758fc5fdddcbc9) - chat data categories *(PR #26 by @aliernfrog)*:

  `getWords`, `getVerbs`, `addWord`, `addVerb`, `deleteWord`, `deleteVerb` were removed and `getChatCategories`, `addChatCategory`, `deleteChatCategory` should be used instead

- due to [`b84f1fe`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/b84f1fe697c1d8f2ff4c9c28e1e3a485d4cd5ff9) - profile view, dynamic actions and info *(commit by @aliernfrog)*:

  `getStatus`, `destroyProcess` and `postEnsicordAddon` were removed, `getDashboard` should be used instead


### ‚ú® New Features
- [`5c2e46b`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/5c2e46b47d9e36961efbcfc2ccef8f73e3cffb4a) - initial predictive back gesture support *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`aee009e`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/aee009eb9da7509f841906bbc75efe6b5797061f) - move logs to its own tab *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`dd8f665`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/dd8f665b227866d4577eb97f44758fc5fdddcbc9) - **api**: chat data categories *(PR #26 by @aliernfrog)*
- [`b84f1fe`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/b84f1fe697c1d8f2ff4c9c28e1e3a485d4cd5ff9) - **dashboard**: profile view, dynamic actions and info *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`d29d484`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/d29d484b9a8bf83cee5abc8ada90ecb405c4e2d7) - **settings**: small redesign, add credits and library list *(commit by @aliernfrog)*

### üêõ Bug Fixes
- [`f338796`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/f3387964ed95d0afe3e37577bd199e2b76bb47e2) - **logs-screen/log-item**: consider smaller size *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`e74667f`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/e74667f46225c69e47725b2ff149548574209965) - navigation transitions *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`6498f2c`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/6498f2cfa47767354a664610cd8ef7dbfedb5587) - **chat**: dont fetch when switching categories *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
- [`512d85b`](https://github.com/aliernfrog/ensi-manager/commit/512d85be2da7dcbf8546ed5c7bcd9c2a4a6a86cc) - only do automatic api calls once *(commit by @aliernfrog)*
